text: Lee Ho (born 14 November 1976) is a South Korean rower. He competed in the men's double sculls event at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1976 births Category:Living people Category:South Korean male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of South Korea Category:Rowers at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
